author: jleroux
msg: A patch from Deepak Dixit "Autocompleter fails if lookup fieldFormName contains (?)" https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OFBIZ-4646
For regenerating issue go to https://demo-trunk.ofbiz.apache.org/facility/control/ReceiveInventory?facilityId=WebStoreWarehouse , enter GZ-1005 and receive.
Now on receive inventory page search "Facility Location" via autocompleter then it will show the lookup screen instead of search result.
